text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits obsolete IRM 1.34.3, Revenue Accounting, Audit Oversight and Analysis.

IRM 1.34.3 is obsolete. It was significantly revised on January 13, 2015, and moved to new section 1.35.14, Financial Accounting, Internal Revenue Service Annual Financial Statement Audit, to more accurately reflect its content and purpose.
